SIMON: I believe
deeply in our cause.

36:54.294 --> 36:58.130
If I give you Channing, I want
the organization to continue.

36:58.165 --> 37:00.365
And I want to run it.

37:00.401 --> 37:02.601
Responsibly.

37:02.636 --> 37:05.670
But I'm going to need funding.

37:14.914 --> 37:18.683
HEWES: I think we can
come to an arrangement.

37:18.719 --> 37:20.819
(banging on door)

37:20.854 --> 37:22.888
GARY: Open the door.

37:27.360 --> 37:28.260
Where is she?

37:28.295 --> 37:29.261
PARSONS: She's not here.

37:29.296 --> 37:30.262
GARY: Bullshit.

37:30.297 --> 37:32.264
PARSONS: You're
wasting your time.

37:32.299 --> 37:34.266
GARY: I know you're
protecting her.

37:34.301 --> 37:35.267
PARSONS: Yes, I am.

37:35.302 --> 37:36.268
She's in a hotel.

37:36.303 --> 37:36.968
GARY: Which one?

37:37.004 --> 37:38.036
PARSONS: I'm not telling you.

37:38.072 --> 37:39.938
GARY: Which fucking hotel?

37:39.973 --> 37:41.873
DENISE: Gary, stop, please.

37:41.909 --> 37:44.009
PARSONS: Jesus, Mom,
go back to your room.

37:44.044 --> 37:46.011
GARY: So, now you're
lying for her?

37:46.046 --> 37:47.012
DENISE: Don't blame Ellen.

37:47.047 --> 37:48.113
GARY: Believe me.

37:48.148 --> 37:49.281
You're the one I blame.

37:49.316 --> 37:51.283
PARSONS: Okay, Dad,
just leave her alone.

37:51.318 --> 37:53.385
GARY: You file for divorce,
and you don't even tell me?

37:53.420 --> 37:55.320
I have to find out through
the fucking mail?

37:55.355 --> 37:57.055
PARSONS: Okay, Dad,
you can leave.

37:57.091 --> 37:58.290
GARY: Shut up!

37:58.325 --> 37:59.424
You listen to me.

37:59.460 --> 38:00.826
There's not gonna be a divorce.

38:00.861 --> 38:01.827
DENISE: Please, just go.

38:01.862 --> 38:02.861
We'll talk later.

38:02.896 --> 38:05.130
GARY: You're gonna
come home with me now.

38:05.165 --> 38:06.231
PARSONS: She's staying here.

38:06.266 --> 38:08.767
GARY: Stop acting like a
fucking child and come home.

38:08.802 --> 38:13.872
PARSONS: Dad, I'm warning... GARY:
You mind your own fucking business.

38:13.907 --> 38:18.009
You come with me now, or I'm gonna
drag your fat ass out of here.

38:18.045 --> 38:19.478
DENISE: Okay, okay,
just stop yelling.

38:19.513 --> 38:20.278
PARSONS: Dad.

38:20.314 --> 38:21.413
GARY: Shut up!

38:21.448 --> 38:23.281
PARSONS: Get the fuck out!

38:23.317 --> 38:30.122
DENISE: Ellen...
PARSONS: Get out!

38:30.157 --> 38:32.657
GARY: What the hell
are you doing?

38:32.693 --> 38:35.627
You think you're gonna
kill your father?

38:35.662 --> 38:36.862
PARSONS: Kill you?

38:36.897 --> 38:38.029
No.

38:38.065 --> 38:41.833
But New York State Law recognizes the
justifiable use of proportional force in

38:41.869 --> 38:43.001
self-defense.

38:43.036 --> 38:46.371
So, I could certainly shoot you
if you don't get out of here.

38:46.406 --> 38:47.973
The arm.

38:48.008 --> 38:49.774
Leg.

38:49.810 --> 38:51.943
Where do you want it, Dad?

38:51.979 --> 38:55.013
I promise you I won't miss.

39:01.254 --> 39:03.288
GARY: This isn't over.

39:12.265 --> 39:15.300
(door opens, closes)

39:36.289 --> 39:38.523
McCLAREN: I'm not
abandoning this leak.

39:38.559 --> 39:41.393
It's too big, too important.

39:44.664 --> 39:46.698
SIMON: Yeah, all right, fine.

39:46.733 --> 39:50.402
But from here on out, Walling
interacts only with me.

40:09.956 --> 40:11.990
(speaking Italian)

40:15.895 --> 40:18.430
HERRESHOFF: Mr. Simon.

40:18.465 --> 40:21.199
SIMON: Thank you for
meeting with me.

40:21.235 --> 40:23.235
HERRESHOFF: Your phone
call piqued my interest.

40:23.270 --> 40:27.592
Can't imagine at McClarenTruth
would want with me.

40:29.962 --> 40:33.063
SIMON: We've been approached by
a source who has evidence

40:33.183 --> 40:35.573
of insider trading at Princefield,

40:36.130 --> 40:39.396
specifically, your Fund 23 division.

40:40.254 --> 40:43.388
HERRESHOFF: What do you
want with me, Mr. Simon?

40:43.423 --> 40:45.757
SIMON: I have a
proposal for you.

40:45.792 --> 40:49.327
Channing McClaren already knows
about the leak, so I can't stop

40:49.363 --> 40:52.631
it, but I'm offering you the chance
to get ahead of the tsunami.

40:52.666 --> 40:55.066
I can delay the leak long enough
for you to build a firewall,

40:55.102 --> 40:57.669
distance yourself
from the trading.

40:57.704 --> 41:01.273
HERRESHOFF: And in
exchange, you want...?

41:01.308 --> 41:05.443
SIMON: I want to get rid
of Channing McClaren.

41:12.285 --> 41:18.423
Once he's gone, I want funding
to keep the organization afloat.

41:18.458 --> 41:23.762
HERRESHOFF: How do you
intend to get rid of him?

41:23.797 --> 41:26.865
SIMON: By including the identity
of the source in the leak.

41:26.900 --> 41:31.903
Channing's entire persona is built
upon the promise of absolute anonymity

41:31.938 --> 41:33.038
for the whistle-blower.

41:33.073 --> 41:36.875
If he violates that,
he'll be ruined.

41:36.910 --> 41:41.346
HERRESHOFF: May I ask
the source's name?

41:41.381 --> 41:44.082
SIMON: Naomi Walling.

42:09.775 --> 42:11.810
(sighs)

43:01.494 --> 43:04.195
(horn honking in distance)

43:10.870 --> 43:13.104
(pigeon cooing)

43:44.904 --> 43:46.938
(wings flapping)

43:55.314 --> 43:57.348
(door bangs open)

44:03.322 --> 44:05.657
PARSONS: Thanks
for the heads-up.

44:05.692 --> 44:07.325
COOPER: You okay?

44:07.360 --> 44:09.461
PARSONS: I'm fine.

44:13.165 --> 44:16.868
PATRICK: What do
you want from me?

44:16.903 --> 44:20.605
PARSONS: I know who
you are, Mr. Scully.

44:20.640 --> 44:22.941
And apparently, you
know who I am.

44:22.976 --> 44:27.245
PATRICK: Never seen you
before in my life.

44:27.280 --> 44:29.881
PARSONS: Strange.

44:29.916 --> 44:36.821
Seeing as you tried to kill me when I
was staying in Patty Hewes' apartment.

44:36.857 --> 44:39.090
Why did you do it?

44:39.125 --> 44:42.594
PATRICK: Look... I ended up
with a knife in my chest.

44:42.629 --> 44:45.563
I'd say we're even.

44:45.599 --> 44:47.632
PARSONS: We're not even.

44:47.667 --> 44:51.369
PATRICK: You want to
hurt me, go ahead.

44:51.404 --> 44:54.105
Put one in the back
of my fucking head.

44:54.140 --> 44:55.340
Just do it already.

44:55.375 --> 44:58.109
PARSONS: That wouldn't
make us even, either.

44:58.144 --> 45:00.545
PATRICK: Well, then
what do you want?

45:00.580 --> 45:03.781
PARSONS: I want to
know who hired you.

45:14.727 --> 45:16.928
You see this?

45:19.331 --> 45:23.067
I had it on me that day.

45:23.103 --> 45:26.771
You see that corner
that's missing?

45:26.806 --> 45:30.108
I had the blood on that tested.

45:30.143 --> 45:32.243
And guess what?

45:32.279 --> 45:34.612
It's your DNA.

45:38.484 --> 45:45.757
I know you started a new life, Mr. Scully,
and you have a wife, a kid...

45:45.792 --> 45:52.130
but if you don't tell me what I
want to know, then it's all over.

45:52.165 --> 45:56.267
You'll never see them again.

45:56.303 --> 46:01.139
I have two homicide detectives
just waiting for my call.

46:09.081 --> 46:12.850
So let me ask you again.

46:12.886 --> 46:15.119
Who hired you?

46:22.094 --> 46:24.996
PATRICK: Patty Hewes.

46:25.031 --> 46:27.231
(footsteps approaching)

46:32.838 --> 46:35.306
MAGGIE: Ms. Hewes will
be with you in moment.

46:35.342 --> 46:37.375
PARSONS: Thank you.

47:06.772 --> 47:09.807
(indistinct voices in distance)

47:43.876 --> 47:47.612
PARSONS: I like your chair.

47:47.647 --> 47:50.014
Thought I'd give it a try.

47:50.050 --> 47:52.016
I need a new one for my office.

47:52.052 --> 47:54.252
HEWES: No, no, no, don't get up.

47:54.287 --> 47:55.753
Sit.

47:55.789 --> 47:58.089
See how it feels.

48:04.530 --> 48:08.466
I wasn't aware that we had
any outstanding business.

48:08.501 --> 48:11.202
PARSONS: We don't.

48:11.237 --> 48:14.439
I didn't think I'd see you
before the trial started, and...

48:14.474 --> 48:17.175
I wanted to wish you luck.

48:17.210 --> 48:19.577
HEWES: Well... (sniffs)

48:21.880 --> 48:24.182
Good luck to you.

48:27.686 --> 48:32.523
PARSONS: It's what
we wanted, isn't it?

48:32.559 --> 48:36.194
A fair fight.

48:36.229 --> 48:39.230
Head to head in a courtroom.

48:41.400 --> 48:43.835
HEWES: Absolutely.

48:50.242 --> 48:53.444
You know, I'm actually glad
you came by because there's

48:53.480 --> 48:57.415
something I wanted to
talk to you about.

48:57.450 --> 48:59.217
PARSONS: What's that?

48:59.252 --> 49:02.987
HEWES: Our conversation
in the airport in Maine.

49:11.330 --> 49:13.831
PARSONS: What about it?

49:16.935 --> 49:22.373
HEWES: Well, as I told you then...
I didn't have anything

49:22.408 --> 49:26.511
to do with your attack.

49:26.546 --> 49:34.118
But... PARSONS: But?

49:34.154 --> 49:38.234
HEWES: But I can understand
why you thought I did.

49:39.692 --> 49:43.614
And I want to apologize
if I was insensitive.

49:46.740 --> 49:48.398
I was just...

49:48.993 --> 49:50.373
surprised...

49:51.468 --> 49:53.518
that you still thought I'd been involved.

49:57.910 --> 50:01.579
PARSONS: I should be
apologizing to you.

50:03.982 --> 50:05.817
I feel stupid.

50:05.852 --> 50:10.621
'Course you had nothing
to do with it.

50:10.657 --> 50:13.090
And I'm sorry.

50:32.344 --> 50:36.681
HEWES: Ah, I just
had a premonition.

50:36.716 --> 50:38.616
PARSONS: Of what?

50:38.651 --> 50:43.421
HEWES: This is the last time you'll
ever set foot in this office.

50:49.695 --> 50:51.729
PARSONS: Maybe.

50:56.335 --> 50:58.736
You never know.

